      "id": 1,
      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nOne row per member \u00d7 card. Sourced from **`reporting.dim_card`** joined to **`reporting.dim_member`**.\n\n| Column | Source | Meaning |\n|--------|--------|--------|\n| Client Member ID | `dim_member.client_member_id` | Your internal member identifier |\n| FIS Person ID | `dim_member.fis_person_id` | FIS-assigned person identifier, stamped by Stage 7 after enrollment |\n| FIS CUID | `dim_member.fis_cuid` | FIS cardholder unique ID, stamped by Stage 7 |\n| FIS Card ID | `dim_card.fis_card_id` | FIS-assigned card number, stamped by Stage 7 |\n| Card Status | `dim_card.card_status` | 1=Active, 2=Suspended, 3=Closed |\n| Start Date | `dim_card.issued_at` | Date card record was created in the pipeline |\n| Activated Date | `dim_card.activated_at` | Date member first used the card (null = not yet activated) |\n\n> **FIS IDs** are null until Stage 7 reconciliation runs against a FIS return file. All 169 test members are reconciled as of 2026-03-31.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3",
      "title": "",
      "type": "text"
    },
